Output docs/demo.gif

Set FontSize 14
Set Width 960
Set Height 540
Set Padding 12
Set Theme "TokyoNight"
Set TypingSpeed 25ms
Set Framerate 20

Hide
Type "clear"
Enter
Show

Sleep 400ms
Type "gitshow replay --commits 4"
Sleep 300ms
Enter

# First commit: watch the typewriter + diff stagger.
Sleep 3500ms

# Bump speed up to fly through the next two commits.
Up
Sleep 150ms
Up
Sleep 150ms

# Watch ~2 commits cycle past.
Sleep 5500ms

# Quit cleanly.
Type "q"
Sleep 600ms
